        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 11. Levinsenia materi (ESFM-POL/2013-1111). A, Lateral view of first two branchial chaetigers; B, Lateral view of second branchial chaetiger, with notopodial postchaetal lob emerging on branchiae; C, Lateral view of middle branchial region; D, Parapodium from posterior region with modified neurochaetae, notopodial postchaetal lobe and lateral sense organ. Scale bar: A, 51 µm; B, 16 µm; C, 42 µm; D, 19 µm. Abbreviations: ant, anterior region; bran, branchiae; lso, lateral sense organ; ntpcl, notopodial postchaetal lobe; post, posterior region." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4438161/files/figure.png" .

